Well, I'm staying here because

00:10:13.260 --> 00:10:16.260
we wanted to demonstrate to you

00:10:16.260 --> 00:10:19.260
the power of this technology

00:10:19.260 --> 00:10:22.260
and so, while I've been speaking,

00:10:22.260 --> 00:10:25.260
you have been scanned.

00:10:25.260 --> 00:10:28.260
(Laughter)

